room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: My office decided to have an after hours activity just to have fun. We choose the museum. This was my first time there and once I saw how the others were solving the clues, I got into it. Had a blast. Would recommend highly.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: Museum heist with co- worker was amazing experience. This was our first time but not the last. The excitement of not knowing what to find next just brought so much adrenaline.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Memphis in Memphis
review: Breakout Memphis was so much fun!!! We loved this escape room! We did the Museum Heist, and loved all the surprises in the room! It was my husband birthday adventure & we had a blast! The location is a little hard to find (based on the address on yalls Facebook page) but we called & they were more than helpful! Can't wait to come back & do another one!! Staff was so friendly as well!!
